Package aima.core.search.framework

Class PrioritySearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.core.search.framework.PrioritySearch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SearchForActions, SearchForStates
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BestFirstSearch, UniformCostSearch
    public class PrioritySearch
extends java.lang.Object
implements SearchForActions, SearchForStates
    Performs search by creating a priority queue based on a given Comparator and feeding it to a given QueueSearch implementation which finally controls the simulated search space exploration.
    Author:
    Ravi Mohan, Ruediger Lunde
